# Final Verification — The Target Demo

After completing the minimum 13-task path (Sprint 1–3):

1. ✅ Open web dispatcher dashboard on laptop
2. ✅ Open guard app on phone via Expo Go
3. ✅ Log in with seeded accounts
4. ✅ Guard walks around → dot moves on web map in real time
5. ✅ Guard presses panic → alert fires on web within 3 seconds
6. ✅ Guard clocks in → shift goes active on web
7. ✅ Guard scans checkpoint → marker updates on web map

**Everything in this roadmap builds toward that outcome.**
